uld want for John Walker.<br><br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/utelkandoretelenesis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Telkandore Telenesis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0> at: 2/8/02 4:51:34 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/uladmovonwallace.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ladmovonwallace</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>l33t board camper</span><br>  Posts: 365<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(2/9/02 5:58:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=97.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.send4fun.com/IMAGES/bassethound_playingbanjo_lg_clr.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Strange rules</span><hr size=1> who cares <p>retired poo slinger</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#4D4D4D><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/uwittlesvaseel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>WittlesVaseel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>l33t board camper</span><br>  Posts: 357<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(2/9/02 12:35:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=97.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Strange rules</span><hr size=1> The American was denied the lawyer his parents hired. Last I heard anyways. <br><br>The Australian got the tougher sentence because there are too many crocodile hunter copycat shows now, and we are sending a message. <p><center><img src="http://www.hairpinharpie.addr.com/drink_quiz/images/martini.jpg" border="1" alt="Drink me!"></a><br><a href="http: